Package dk.jakobhandersen.multiregionexporterforcubase

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    UserInterface
    This interface is the 'main' interface and represents the graphic user interface.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AboutDialog
    SWT dialog - the About page showing info about this version etc.
    AudioBite
    Class that represents one audio region that is to be copied from the full file to its own file.
    AudioBiteStartComparator
    Comparator to be used when sorting a list of AudioBites based on their start time
    AudioOutputter
    (Thread) Class that does the actual outputting of file extracted from the input file.
    Constants
    Class that holds constants used in the project
    CubaseTrackXMLSaxParseHandler
    Extension of DefaultHandler to be used with SAXParser.
    Debug
    Class that handles print calls for debugging
    ExporterEngine
    The class that coordinates the actual functionality of the application.
    InputAudioFile
    Class holding info about an audio file
    InputAudioFileBuilder
    A class based on Thread that builds an InputAudioFile Uses SoXi to read audio properties
    MultiRegionExporterForCubase
    This class is the 'main' class and represents the graphic user interface.
    OutputtingDialog
    SWT dialog - Showing that the application is busy outputting the files.
    ReadingAudioDialog
    SWT dialog Showing that the application is busy reading an audio input file.
    Utils
    Class that contains utility function(s)
    WaveformGenerator
    Class based on Thread that handles the reading of waveform data.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ElementType
    Enumeration to define the different relevant element types in the Cubase track XML file
    EngineEvent
    Different types of events to be sent from ExporterEngine to UserInterface
    TimeFormat
    Enumeration that defines different time formats
    UserMessageType
    Enumeration that defines different types of messages to the user
